OL,5, A French tourist has been jailed for   
OL,6, eight years for spying by a court in   
OL,7, Iran, his lawyer in Paris has said.    
OL,9,FBenjamin Briere, 36, was arrested in   
OL,10,FMay 2020 after flying a drone near the 
OL,11,FIran-Turkmenistan border.              
OL,13,FFrance's foreign ministry called his   
OL,14,Fconviction "unacceptable" and said it  
OL,15,Fhad "no basis in fact".                
OL,17,FA lawyer for Mr Briere, Philippe       
OL,18,FValent, said his client had grown "more
OL,19,Fand more weak" from a hunger strike    
OL,20,Fwhich he began in December.            
